casebody.data:
Julian Andres VALDIVIESO
v.
Donnie HARRISON No. 7P18 Supreme Court of North Carolina. January 8, 2018 Julian Andres Valdivieso, for Valdivieso, Julian Andres.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Petitioner on the 8th of January 2018 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Wake County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 8th of January 2018."
